name: Kelly
description: I’m looking for a nice man with right qualities of a serious and intelligent man. He should be kind, loving, generous, well-educated and sincere in his intentions to me. I’m searching someone special, who has similar interests and views for a life and who wants to create a family with me. He should be faithful and honest. I don’t support any lie and cheating. So, I hope that I will find someone really good here. I’m open to new serious acquaintance. Don’t shy to contact with me if you liked my profile.
